The paper deals with information hiding in images, which is a topic related to computer security (cs.CR) and computer vision (cs.CV). The use of generative adversarial networks (GANs) is a machine learning technique, which falls under the categories of multimedia (cs.MM), machine learning (cs.LG), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
